# 🌐 Project Title: Food order Website

## 📖 Description
A simple and elegant portfolio website created using **HTML** and **CSS**. This project showcases my skills, projects, and contact information in a visually appealing design.

---

## 🌟 Features
- Responsive design for all devices (mobile, tablet, desktop).
- Clean and modern layout.
- Smooth hover effects and animations.
- Organized sections for **About**, **Projects**, and **Contact**.

